\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li1208\ri0\lin1208\rin0\fi-760\sl360\slmult1\qj [27] \tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\cf0\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls2\aspalpha\li1208\ri0\lin1208\rin0\fi-760\rtlch\af7\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f0\fs24\lang1033\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0{ The principal arguments advanced by counsel for the accused in support of their contention that the imposition of the death penalty for murder is a "cruel, inhuman or degrading punishment," were that the death sentence is an affront to human dignity, is in
