\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s9\cf0\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\li1563\ri1714\lin1563\rin1714\fi0\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f0\fs21\lang1033\loch\f0\fs21\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs21\lang1033\i0\b0 [t]here is strong ground for believing, having regard to the limited extent to which the death penalty advances any valid penological objectives and the serious invasion of human dignity it engenders, that the death penalty cannot, except in exceptional ci
rcumstances, be justified in this country.{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s8\cf0\sl360\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\li283\ri0\lin283\rin0\fi-283\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch {\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 Id. at 202 (per La Forest, J)(L'Heureux-Dube and Gonthier, JJ concurring). }}}
