\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s9\cf0\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\li1563\ri1714\lin1563\rin1714\fi0\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f0\fs21\lang1033\loch\f0\fs21\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs21\lang1033\i0\b0 The adoption of this Constitution lays the secure foundation for the people of South Africa to transcend the divisions and strife of the past, which generated gross violations of human rights, the transgression of humanitarian principles in violent conflic
ts and a legacy of hatred, fear, guilt and {\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\i\loch\i revenge}. }
