\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s9\cf0\sl360\slmult1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\li1563\ri1714\lin1563\rin1714\fi0\ql\rtlch\af4\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f0\fs21\lang1033\loch\f0\fs21\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f0\fs21\lang1033\i0\b0 vicissitudes of political controversy, to place them beyond the reach of majorities... and to establish them as legal principles to be applied by the courts. One\'92s right to life.... and other fundamental rights may not be submitted to vote; they depend on 
